        public javax.vecmath.Vector3d nextVec()
        Description copied from interface: VectorIterator
        Returns: null if there are no more points in the sequence, else a new Vector3d whose value is the next point. The returned Vector3d may be modified by the caller. The same Vector3d may be written to again on the subsequent call to nextVec().
